Author: MidoriKami
Name: DailyDuty
Punchline: Easily Track Daily and Weekly tasks.
Description: Automatically track and complete many daily and weekly tasks.
Changelog:
This took several days of programming, experimenting, and learning to complete, but it's here now!

Added: Options for smaller/more condensed Timers Bars (Thx Chuggo)
Added: Option to suppress any messages tagged "Debug"

Fixed: All modules now check if the module is enabled before sending notifications
Fixed: Duty Roulette detecting any zone change as a "roulette complete" change
Fixed: Fashion Report going negative on first turn-in for the week
Fixed: Purges "Zero" player from older configs to prevent crashes

Added: Wondrous Tails Overlay for Duty Finder

Shows the status of the duty relative to your Wondrous Tails book
Golden Clover - Can complete for a Wondrous Tails Stamp
Faded Clover - Already completed in your Wondrous Tails Book

Added: Duty Roulette Coloring
Added: Configurable Color options for Duty Roulettes
